      "writtenOn": "2019-03-09T06:48:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "this makes me said :( 1 end to end test is less to read, less to modify in the future and gives the same signal:\nsort(Tue 4pm\nMon 10am\nSat # defaulting to 0 am\nFriday 6pm PST (ie 3am Sat UTC)\nTue 5am)\n\u003d\u003e Mon,Tue10am,Tue4pm,Sat0am,Friday6pmPST\n\nAlterntaively, if you adopt SortSlice suggestion, test just the Less function here.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 40,
        "startChar": 1,
        "endLine": 139,
        "endChar": 3
      },
      "revId": "2ada2df4b75092550ad59dc379bd5d57edcbcdff",
